# AI Risk Posture Summary

Reporting Period: Q1  
Prepared By: Governance & Compliance  
Date: 2/23/2026

---

## Executive Overview

The organization currently operates eight documented AI systems across Corporate IT, Human Resources, Procurement, Operations, Finance, Development, and Customer Support functions.

An AI governance assessment was conducted to evaluate:

- Data exposure
- Regulatory impact
- Access control maturity
- Operational and financial risk

